<p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwg6l7x/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="Nike NBA克里夫兰骑士队女式速干T恤" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/09/5f58806bd50756853.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">来看看衣服背面，Cleveland Cavaliers队名是黄色印着的，相比之前Lebron那件，没有印号码，也就少了球员已经转会带来的尴尬。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwg6l7x/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img alt="Nike NBA克里夫兰骑士队女式速干T恤" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/09/5f58806f976e4159.jpg-270_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">看看洗标，我买的XXL才175/96A，建议100cm胸围，着实偏小。面料的话，由58%棉和42%聚酯纤维组成。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwg6l7x/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="Nike NBA克里夫兰骑士队女式速干T恤" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/09/5f5880725f2413548.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">量一下尺码，平铺胸围也才47cm，乘以二连96cm都没到。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwg6l7x/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img alt="Nike NBA克里夫兰骑士队女式速干T恤" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/09/5f58806f9b6329230.jpg-270_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">衣长为67cm。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwg6l7x/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img alt="Nike NBA克里夫兰骑士队女式速干T恤" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/09/5f588070800943710.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">真人兽，还好买大一号，不然就像<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/jinshenyi/" target="_blank">紧身衣</a>了。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/adwg6l7x/pic_13/' target='_blank'><img alt="Nike NBA克里夫兰骑士队女式速干T恤" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/09/5f588072acbd98562.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">照片晒完，总结收尾：</p><ol class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><li><p itemprop="description">价格很便宜；</p></li><li><p itemprop="description">官方正版授权；</p></li><li><p itemprop="description">速干透气面料，很舒适；</p></li><li><p itemprop="description">尺码偏