➜FUTURE FUNK x《多啦 A 梦》50 周年限量手表，“翻盖”是灵魂
https://post.smzdm.com/p/aooz4knr/	21087
<blockquote><p itemprop="description">本资讯信息、图片均来源于FUTURE FUNK官网</p></blockquote><p itemprop="description">为庆祝着名<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/manhua/" target="_blank">漫画</a>家藤子・F・不二雄创作的《<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/10901/" data-brandid="10901" target="_blank">哆啦A梦</a>》连载50周年，FUTURE FUNK x《多啦 A 梦》推出了一款以哆啦A梦为设计主题的<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/nanbiao/" target="_blank">腕表</a>，现已开始售卖。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aooz4knr/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="FUTURE FUNK x《多啦 A 梦》50 周年限量手表，“翻盖”是灵魂" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202009/10/5f59bb8f77a94903.png_e680.jpg" _size="132790"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">腕表分为女款的 Pan-Paka-Pan 和男款 ROLLER 两种款式，女款的 Pan-Paka-Pan 采用的是哆啦A梦的铃铛造型，翻盖设计，闭合状态呈现出召猫铃的样式，红色的表带和漫画里如出一辙。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aooz4knr/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img alt="FUTURE FUNK x《多啦 A 梦》50 周年限量手表，“翻盖”是灵魂" src="https://a.zdmimg.com/202009/10/5f59bc27ddaf0682.png_e680.jpg" _size="472279"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aooz4knr/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img alt="FUTURE FUNK x《多啦 A 梦》50 周年限量手表，“翻盖”是灵魂" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202009/10/5f59bc2bde82d2885.png_e680.jpg" _size="701066"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">表盘上哆啦A梦的眼睛，根据时间的变化展示不同的表情，非常有趣。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aooz4knr/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img alt="FUTURE FUNK x《多啦 A 梦》50 周年限量手表，“翻盖”是灵魂" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202009/10/5f59bc4fb7fb63501.png_e680.jpg" _size="130498"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description">男款的 ROLLER 腕表属于 20 世纪 70 年代流行的 Space Time 风格，表面上的时间则是以滚筒的形式进行展示，贴合复古<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/35731/" data-brandid="35731" target="_blank">爱好</a>者的审美。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/aooz4knr/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="FUTURE FUNK x《多啦 A 梦》50 周年限量手表，“翻盖”是灵魂" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202009/10/5f59bc925cc35491.png_e680.jpg" _size="699020"  title="" data-title=""/></a></p><p itemprop="description"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(187, 2, 0);"><strong>这款腕表售价为 24000 日元（不含税，约人民币1550元），感兴趣的值友们可以去 FUTURE FUNK 官网看看~  </strong></span></p><dir><span class="embed-card main-site " style=""><span class="embed-card-logo"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'FFDR-BK-PB–FUTUREFUNK','id':'2589487' , 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'无', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'futurefunk-watch.com','dimension9':'news','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang','cd49':'无'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class="" href="http://www.futurefunk-watch.com/product/ffdr-bk-pb"  rel="nofollow" ><img ol  alt="FUTURE FUNK x《多啦 A 梦》50 周年限量手表，“翻盖”是灵魂" class="" src="https://qna.smzdm.com/202009/10/5f59be55bb5061398.png_a200.jpg"/></a></span><span class="embed-card-info"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'FFDR-BK-PB–FUTUREFUNK','id':'2589487' , 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'无', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'futurefunk-watch.com','dimension9':'news','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension25':'无','dimension64':'yuanchuang','cd49':'无'});if(typeof change_direct_url != 'undefined' && change_direct_url instanceof Function){change_direct_url(this)}" class="" href="http://www.futurefunk-watch.com/product/ffdr-bk-pb"  rel="nofollow" ><span class="card-name">FFDR-BK-PB–FUTUREFUNK</span></a><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><a target="_blank" onclick="gtmAddToCart({'name':'FFDR-BK-PB–FUTUREFUNK','id':'2589487' , 'price':'无','brand':'无' ,'mall':'无', 'category':'无/无/无/无','metric1':'无','dimension10':'futurefunk-watch.com','dimension9':'news','dimension11':'无','dimension20':'无','dimension2